# Current Architecture (Before Hardening)

```mermaid
graph TB
    subgraph "Branch Offices (9 cities)"
        B1[Branch Router]
        B2[Branch Users]
    end
    
    subgraph "Data Center"
        subgraph "Server Segment (Compromised)"
            WEB[Web Server<br/>Customer Portal]
            DB[(Database<br/>Customer Data)]
            APP[App Server<br/>Internal Tools]
        end
        FW[Firewall<br/>Minimal Rules]
    end
    
    subgraph "Cloud Footprint"
        CLOUD[Cloud Resources<br/>Public IPs]
    end
    
    INTERNET((Internet))
    
    B1 --> FW
    B2 --> WEB
    WEB --> DB
    WEB --> APP
    APP --> INTERNET
    FW --> CLOUD
    
    style WEB fill:#ff9999
    style DB fill:#ff9999
    style APP fill:#ff9999
    style INTERNET fill:#ffcccc
